This is the full run of Flare Adventures by Heroic Publishing, 31 total issues. Most of these copies seem to have been converted from pdf versions by Helga Phugly; these are relatively low-res editions. However, for a few issues I was able to find true DCP versions of the scans; the scanners are all listed in the individual filenames. This fills a request from KAT. Thanks to all the scanner groups for their efforts, please seed and enjoy! :-)
